                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "One of the main design choices we faced was the transport protocol we would use to train and evaluate MARLIN. The decision fell on a custom transport protocol because it is much simpler to integrate with MARLIN than TCP. Additionally, a custom protocol enables greater flexibility in terms of retrieving the information required to encode the agent state."
